SAFARI CLUB INTERNATIONAL, et al., petitioners,
v.
Sally JEWELL, Secretary of the Interior, et al. No. 13-142. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, In re Polar Bear Endangered Species Act Listing and Section 4(d) Rule Litigation-MDL No. 1993, 709 F.3d 1 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.
